This node requires apcupsd to be running. A sample configuration file for
the SmartUps 100XL is included in the apcupsd.conf file. On Ubuntu, copy
this file into /etc/apcupsd, and then start apcupsd.

sudo apt-get install apcupsd
sudo cp apcupsd.conf /etc/apcupsd
sudo /etc/init.d/apcupsd start

apcupsd's possible error messages will appear in /var/log/messages
